<div class="actions">
  <div>
    <p class="page-kicker">🏆 Disputa geral</p>
    <h1 class="page-title">Ranking da zoeira</h1>
  </div>
</div>

<div class="hype-card mb-4">
  <p class="text-lg font-black text-slate-950">Aqui nao tem amizade: quem pontua sobe, quem erra vira pauta. 🔥</p>
  <p class="muted">Placares exatos dao moral. Resultado certo evita passar vergonha.</p>
</div>

<div class="table-shell overflow-x-auto">
  <table class="data-table">
    <thead>
      <tr>
        <th>Posicao</th>
        <th>Participante</th>
        <th>Pontos</th>
        <th>ADcoins</th>
        <th>Na gaveta</th>
        <th>Acertou o rumo</th>
      </tr>
    </thead>
    <tbody>
      <% @users.each_with_index do |user, index| %>
        <tr>
          <td>
            <span class="<%= index < 3 ? "medal-pill" : "score-pill" %>">
              <%= ["🥇", "🥈", "🥉"][index] || "##{index + 1}" %>
            </span>
          </td>
          <td class="font-black text-slate-950"><%= user.name %> <%= index.zero? ? "👑" : "" %></td>
          <td class="font-black text-emerald-800"><%= user.total_points %> pts</td>
          <td class="font-bold text-amber-700"><%= user.adcoins_balance %> 🪙</td>
          <td><%= user.exact_hits %> 🎯</td>
          <td><%= user.result_hits %> ✅</td>
        </tr>
      <% end %>
    </tbody>
  </table>
</div>
